{"tid":2088702,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人想入Toyota Raize?","createTime":"2020-07-01T09:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T09:24:08.000Z","uid":38556,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cb20e2394ccdf1612bac9f48596586890d8a8127","tid":2088702,"uid":38556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.topgearhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Raize-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.topgearhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2FRaize-2.jpg&h=bb77b5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.topgearhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Raize-TRD%E6%94%B9%E8%A3%9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.topgearhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2FRaize-TRD%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%25A3%259D.jpg&h=8cf9d6c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前豐田在東京車展同時發表Toyota Raize和Daihatsu Rocky，從機械結構上睇，兩部近乎一模一樣，都是採用同一底盤DNGA（Daihatsu New Global Architecture），引擎為1公升turbo，配D-CVT波箱，前輪驅動，而外形也是餅印，似是一部小型RAV4，體積為3,995 x 1,695 x 1,620mm，短過Audi Q2同Volkswagen T-Cross，兩者車章和鬼面罩設計略有不同，Rocky的賣相會相較Raize低調和傳統一點。車廂方面就更加一式一樣，由中控台錶板去到後座空間都完全似十足，尾箱容量有369公升，廠方稱屬同級最大。Raize和Rocky一樣可選配四驅Dynamic Torque Control及一系列的Smart Assist安全系統，例如是車輛碰撞煞停和泊車輔助。兩部車同時亦推出Powerful Style、Sporty Style和Elegance Style三款包圍，另有原廠配件，包括發光中控、無線手機充電座、尾箱收納、皮革軚盤等，Raize更有TRD飾件，適合喜歡玩個人化的車迷。講埋最重要的車價，Toyota Raize &yen;1,679,000起跳，Daihatsu Rocky則為1,705,000&yen;起。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.topgearhk.com/2019/11/07/toyota-raize-vs-daihatsu-rocky%E6%97%A5%E7%B3%BBsuv%E9%AC%A5%E7%8E%A9style/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.topgearhk.com%2F2019%2F11%2F07%2Ftoyota-raize-vs-daihatsu-rocky%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25B3%25BBsuv%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E7%258E%25A9style%2F&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffblm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=bbd9413a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.topgearhk.com/2019/11/07/toyota-raize-vs-daihatsu-rocky%E6%97%A5%E7%B3%BBsuv%E9%AC%A5%E7%8E%A9style/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://keyauto.my/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Toyota-Raize-Modellista-Advance-Blast-Style-02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkeyauto.my%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2FToyota-Raize-Modellista-Advance-Blast-Style-02.jpg&h=bc991326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://keyauto.my/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Toyota-Raize-Modellista-Advance-Blast-Style-03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkeyauto.my%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2FToyota-Raize-Modellista-Advance-Blast-Style-03.jpg&h=703313b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f65fd1a92c7d7d3948768c474f3dd14a000a5c","tid":2088702,"uid":22224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入到香港埋單貴過架窮撚RAV4<br />\n應該無人會買....."},{"pid":"36d6a16dbc92e0f3ae27c1e259a7a9ea7f05bbf5","tid":2088702,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"水貨由頭到出牌 你當大約13算<br />\n過廿萬點會有人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4fe19212583eec3b9d93085cc930aa5b1cf0f4","tid":2088702,"uid":38556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6f65fd1a92c7d7d3948768c474f3dd14a000a5c","tid":2088702,"uid":22224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入到香港埋單貴過架窮撚RAV4<br />\n應該無人會買....."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"睇返日本官網價錢最齋既版本計仲平過部spade"},{"pid":"88bd4ea5157487c2f65d46cee13b9315a75835dc","tid":2088702,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b4fe19212583eec3b9d93085cc930aa5b1cf0f4","tid":2088702,"uid":38556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6f65fd1a92c7d7d3